  <a class="overlay-back" href="/love-your-neighbors/takeaways/">&#8592; Back to Takeaways</a>
  <a class="overlay-close" href="/" aria-label="Close">&times;</a>

  <div class="takeaways-content">
    <Fragment set:html={"<span class=\"takeaways-tag\">Love Your Neighbors</span>\n<h1 class=\"takeaways-title\">Asking Good Questions</h1>\n<p style=\"font-size:.9rem;color:#7A7368;font-style:italic;margin-bottom:2.5rem;font-family:'EB Garamond',serif\">Fun conversation starters and sincere questions that build real connection</p>\n<div class=\"dd-topic-list\"><a class=\"dd-topic-link\" href=\"#dd-fun-questions\">Fun Questions</a><a class=\"dd-topic-link\" href=\"#dd-sincere-questions\">Sincere Questions</a></div>\n\n<div class=\"dd-category\" id=\"dd-fun-questions\"><div class=\"dd-category-title\">Fun Questions</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you were a dictator of a small island nation, what crazy dictator stuff would you do?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;re three things you would literally cut off your own pinky for?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you had a HUD (heads up display) that showed three stats about any person you looked at, what three stats would you want it to show?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If all your exes got together, what&#x27;s one complaint about you that they would all agree on?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could get the truth and inside scoop on any unsolved mystery, historical secret, or cold case in history, which one would you want to know about?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could be a contestant on any game show or reality TV show, past or present, which show would you pick?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Which pictures best encapsulate the last year of your life?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you devoted the next year to making as much money as possible above all else, how would you do it?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What are the three most important things on your bucket list?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What crime would you be most likely to wind up in prison for?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Name three things that you&#x27;re &quot;too good for.&quot; i.e. bottom-shelf liquors, certain fast food chains, single ply toilet paper, middle-seats on an airplane</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could have a video of any one event in your life, what event would you choose?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s the most expensive mistake you&#x27;ve ever made?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What would a world populated by clones of you be like?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could pair up any two single people you know, who would you pick?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Are you smarter than your parents? If so, when do you think you became smarter?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could freeze your spouses physical appearance at one age, but you would grow older, what age would you pick?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If your sexual performance was reviewable on TripAdvisor, what would the ratings and reviews say?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you had to elect one of your friends to be president, who would it be and why?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What is the last dream you had that you can remember?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could change one law, what would it be?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you were given 1000 dollars and told that you had to spend it today, what would you buy?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If a blind man asked you to characterize your physical appearance in detail, how would you describe yourself?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s the craziest night you&#x27;ve had with a bottle of tequila?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you lived in medieval times, which occupation would you choose?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could choose your spouses next partner on your deathbed, who would you recommend?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Given the choice of anyone in the world, who would you want as your dinner guest?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s the coolest tattoo you&#x27;ve ever seen? What tattoo would you get if it only lasted 2 years?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Name the most underrated movie.</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">For $365,000, would you be willing to have terrifying nightmares every night for a year?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you had 400 years to live, what different jobs would you want to try out in your lifetime?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Which 1900&#x27;s era would you travel back to? Why?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you had 1% more control over your spouse or significant other, would your life/relationship be marginally better? What about 50%? 99%?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What is your earliest memory?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could slip your spouse a single pill that rewired one personality trait or habit with zero side-effects, what would the pill do?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you HAD to get a bumper sticker, what would it be or what would it say?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Build the perfect city from scratch using places and parts of cities that you&#x27;ve already visited. What would it include?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If both were offered, would you choose to have a live-in massage therapist or a live-in chef?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What is the single best TV episode of all time? Which TV series had the best final season finale?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you were going to start a business, who would you want as your co-founder?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s the strangest date you&#x27;ve ever been on?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What are your pet peeves?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Which close relative do you like the least, and why?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Would you be more shocked to find out that ten years from now you changed political parties, or that you gained 100lbs?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What random memories do you still have about your life between 6th and 8th grade?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Which of your friend&#x27;s names suits them the best? How about the least?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could abolish one piece of modern technology, what would it be and why?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What apocalyptic dystopia do you think is most likely? What would be your tactic to survive?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What would you rather have leaked to the public: your nude photos or a journal containing your most private thoughts?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Of all the people you know platonically, who do you think is the best in bed?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you weren&#x27;t related to your brothers and sisters, would you still be friends with them? Why or why not?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could have one thing made out of pure gold, what would you choose?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you had to eat the cooking of one person you know personally for the rest of your life, whose would you want it to be?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What are you looking forward to the most this week? This year?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">In your opinion, what topics of conversation do I get most enthusiastic about?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What do you remember most about high school? college? graduation day? first day of work? proposing? wedding? last major breakup? meeting the people you are with right now?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If your child were to be boring, stupid, or ugly, which one would you prefer? Would your choice depend on the child&#x27;s gender?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Which of your friends could you immediately identify, even if they inhabited a different body?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you are going to blog what would you blog about?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could learn the total number of hours you have spent in your life doing one thing, what would it be?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could choose someone you know to be a guest on a television show, who would it be, and on which show?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">For $30,000 would you go for 2 months without washing, brushing your teeth, shampooing, or even using deodorant? Assume you can&#x27;t tell anyone why.</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s your fondest childhood memory? And what is your most treasured adulthood memory?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could commission any living author to write a new book, who would you choose and what would you have them write about?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What crazy news headline do you think you will be reading about in the following year?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Would you accept $2 million to leave the country and never set foot in it again? What would be the minimum amount to seriously tempt you to take this step?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you had to name a single song or album that you most associate with a particular period of your life, what song would you choose, and from what year?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you got transported back to the year 2000, and could start a Youtube channel, what kind of content would you create?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could own a single prop from any film ever made, what would it be?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Which famous person do you think you easily could have been best friends with?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Which sport, game, or activity do you win in most?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">How would you describe your first kiss in three words?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What legislation would have to be passed before you decide to pack up and move to another country?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Of the people you know personally, who is truly 1 in 8 billion?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could shop for free at one store, which one would you choose?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">How old would you be if you didn&#x27;t know how old you are?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Where have you had such a bad experience that you&#x27;ll never go back?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Who were your childhood idols?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you had to choose three people you know to help you survive the apocalypse, who would you recruit?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What do you anticipate social-media, school, work, health care, government, cities will look like in 100 years?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could ask the President one question, what would it be?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">How often do you stay up past 3 a.m.?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s your go-to strategy to distract or entertain yourself?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Have you ever had a crush on a teacher?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What is the highest grade-level that you feel like you would be qualified to teach in any school subject?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could grant one wish to another person, who would you give it to and why?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What was the most embarrassing thing that happened to you as a child?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Build the perfect hotel from scratch. What would it include?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Between you and your significant other, who could amass more followers as an influencer if you both made it your life mission?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What behavioral trait did you inherit more than any other from your mom and dad?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Which grandparent did you inherit more physical traits from than the others?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could snap your fingers and move someone&#x27;s home instantly closer to yours, whose home would you move?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you didn&#x27;t work, how much TV would you watch every day?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could remove one marking from your skin, which one would it be?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If the other quality could stay consistent, would you rather get uglier or dumber with time?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you had to nominate the best-dressed person you know, who would win?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you were a superhero but could only have superpowers that weren&#x27;t already taken, what powers would you choose, and what would your superhero name be?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Which of your friends, if they went all in, would experience the most success as a stripper/chippendale dancer?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you had to give up your favorite food forever, what is the minimum amount of money you would demand in return?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What is something that is popular now that annoys you?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Which of your friends&#x27; personalities is closest to that of their pet&#x27;s?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you suddenly found yourself in the limelight as a political figure or a key public role, which photos from your past would you have to worry about the most?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What is your favorite documentary?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">You have to relive one day of your life forever. Which day do you choose?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you had a personal mascot, what would your mascot be?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s the most trouble you&#x27;ve ever gotten yourself into?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">When do you want to retire? What do you want to do when you retire?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could live in a past era just so you could wear the clothes in fashion at the time, when would it be?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If someone gave you enough money to start a business - no strings attached - what kind of business would you want to start and why?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Who is the most interesting person that you have met?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What piece of entertainment do you wish you could erase from your mind so that you could experience it again for the first time?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could have your license plate say anything at all, what would it be?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you were given $50,000, and the only rule was to maximize both your short-term and long-term happiness, how would you spend it?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">How did you torment your siblings as a kid?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you were a doctor, which speciality would you choose?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What would be the most effective way for someone to seduce you?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Out of the cities that you&#x27;ve been to, which one would make for the best honeymoon? The best bachelor party? The best family trip? The best city to revisit by yourself?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could have any number of kids, how many would you choose to have, and of what gender?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you had the ability to enter someone&#x27;s mind in this room for a few hours and thoroughly explore their thoughts, memories, experiences, and motivations, who would you choose and why?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you had to put all your money into a single asset (not S&amp;P 500 or Dow) for the following year, which one would you choose?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Would you rather be a jack of many trades or a master of one?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could have the chance to see what has become of one childhood friend, who would you choose to find out about?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What would be the most realistic scenario for you becoming famous?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could instantly download the brain from any one person, and upload all of the information and knowledge into your brain, who&#x27;s brain would you choose?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s the last job that you would ever take? Would you take this job if you&#x27;d get paid $10k/Week?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What are you most sensitive about and why?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s one of the biggest life lessons you&#x27;ve learned so far?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you had to pay one hundred dollars for every time you thought of sex in any form, how long would it be before you went bankrupt?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s your favorite holiday and why?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Is there anyone whom you obsessively dislike?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Who is your favorite comedian? Who is your favorite actor/actress?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could have any option/feature added to your automobile, what would it be?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What would constitute a &quot;perfect day&quot; for you?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s the best metaphor for life in your opinion?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you were to spend the rest of your life in the company of a single type of animal, which would you choose?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could rid the earth of one thing, what would it be?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could have any view in the world visible from your bed, what would it be?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Which job would you take if you had to choose between being a tow-truck driver, a corrections officer, or a door-to-door salesman?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If happiness was the national currency, what kind of work would make you rich?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Who is your favorite and least favorite person to compete against?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What TV show are you ashamed to admit you watch?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Would you rather have a great wardrobe or an amazing car?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you had to choose your spouse based on their parents (your in-laws), who would you marry?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">When you look in a mirror, what&#x27;s the first thing you check?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s the best live musical performance you have ever attended?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Do you have a favorite sexual fantasy? If so, what would you give to have it granted?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Which one of you could go the longest without technology and why?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What has been the best year of your life so far?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you had to permanently double or halve your partner&#x27;s appetite for sex, which would you pick? What about your own?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you were going to direct a movie, what would your movie be about? If you were going to be in the movie, would you want the plot to be the same?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Do you believe in ghosts or evil spirits? Would you be willing to spend a night alone in a remote, supposedly haunted house?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you had unlimited funds to produce an investigative documentary, what issue or subject matter would you choose to expose?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you never had to work again, how would you spend your time?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s the pettiest or most trivial attribute that you screen for when looking for a partner?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Build the perfect home from scratch. What would it include?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could have witnessed one event from your ancestry&#x27;s history, what would you want to see?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What one eye-opening experience should every person have?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Who would be the three most likely people to murder you?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">You are given 10 seconds to talk to your dog/cat without any language or communication barriers. What do you say?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What &quot;old person&quot; things do you do?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Who&#x27;s the most attractive 70+ year old you know? What about 50+? What about 30+?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What was your last Google search?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What qualities do all of your friends have in common?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What company do you despise?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What would be an accurate tag line for the last year of your life?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What sport could you play the longest in a televised game without anyone discovering you aren&#x27;t a professional athlete?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you had to limit yourself to only one clothing store, where would you choose to shop?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could snap your fingers and be fluent in one language, which language would you choose?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What chip flavor doesn&#x27;t exist that you would be interested in trying?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">In which situations from the past do you wish you could have thrown down a smoke bomb and disappeared?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could become brilliant by having a visible scar stretching from your mouth to your ear, would you?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What product do you wish a company would make a &quot;smart&quot; version of?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What would you do if all of your Google search history was posted publicly to all of your social media profiles?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Who would be your groomsmen / bridesmaids today?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could make a weird thing socially acceptable, what would that thing be?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What song do you find yourself singing most often and why?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Which of your scars has the best story behind it?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What topic would you be most embarrassed to be publicly quizzed on?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Whats one of the best cheat codes at your company, in your industry, or in your specific position?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Where would you rather be from?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could bring one musician back from the dead, who would it be and why?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">As the only human left on Earth, what would you do?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If a movie was made about your life, what situation would be the climax of it?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Whats the most realistic conspiracy theory you can come up with about someone you know?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What do you have to resist spending too much money on?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What was the best thing that happened to you last week?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What could you give a 40-minute presentation on with absolutely no preparation?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What is something that is considered a luxury that you don&#x27;t think you could live without?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Which of these is the ultimate scam? Multi-level marketing schemes, Timeshare contracts, Textbook edition updates, Free trials that ask for credit card details, Extended warranties, Printers with expensive ink, Rapid weight loss pills, or Student loans for liberal art schools?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Under what circumstances would you attempt a citizens arrest?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What movie universe would be the worst to live out your life in?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s the largest crowd you have ever spoken to or performed in front of?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Who would be the worst person to be stuck in an elevator with? How about the best?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could bring back one TV show that was canceled what would you bring back?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What song always puts you in a good mood?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What excuse do you use most often to avoid going to events?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What is your favorite article of clothing that you own?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could make a holiday, what would it be like? What traditions would it have?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could add any art piece from any museum to your home, what would it be and where would you display it?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What do you think is the most universally hated thing in all of human history?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s a TV show that you used to love but not many people remember?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s one thing you&#x27;re always willing to pay the extra price for?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could sell your fingers, the first going for 10 dollars and each finger payout increasing by a factor of 10, how many would you sell?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What 1st world &quot;problem&quot; do you complain about that&#x27;s actually a 3rd world luxury?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What is the best documentary you have ever watched?</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"dd-category\" id=\"dd-sincere-questions\"><div class=\"dd-category-title\">Sincere Questions</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s a common trait shared by everyone you&#x27;ve dated?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Do you strive more for security, accomplishment, success, love, power, or excitement?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What do you like most about the person sitting across from you?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What do you miss about being a kid?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">In what ways do you tend to be a bit dramatic?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Who is your biggest fan?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What is the best or most worthwhile investment you&#x27;ve ever made? Could be an investment of money, time, energy, or other resource.</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Which physical characteristic of yours most resembles your mother or father? Now which emotional characteristic?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What would you like to be appreciated more for?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s one phone call, event, or meeting that changed your life?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">In what ways, both good and bad, is your partner different from when you met them?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;ve you&#x27;ve been thinking about this week more than anything else?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s one thing you&#x27;re deeply proud of - but would never put on your r�sum�?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Are you right about everything? If no, then what are you wrong about? If you don&#x27;t know, then explain why don&#x27;t you know?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s the nicest thing anyone has ever done for you?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">How is the person that you are dating/married to different from the person you envisioned yourself being married to before you knew them?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">When you think of the word &quot;successful,&quot; who&#x27;s the first person that comes to mind and why?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What is the key issue facing America right now? What about for your state? Your city? Your company? Your family?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Out of all the couples you know personally, which would be the best to go camping with, go clubbing with, go tailgating with, start a business with, go on a wine tour with, travel overseas with?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s the most important ingredient of human beauty?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s the most physically painful thing you&#x27;ve ever experienced?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s your perception of how other people view you?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could relive any single family outing in your life, what would it be?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Which qualities do you most appreciate about your significant other?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s some of the best advice you&#x27;ve ever gotten?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Whose funeral did you most recently attend? What were they like and what do you miss most about them?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What are your most common sources of unhappiness?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;re three things you want to do before you die?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What compliment do you most often receive? What compliments do you most often give?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you had to work abroad for a summer, what would you take a job doing?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s the most offensive (but true) thing someone could say to you?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Suppose you were never allowed to see your best friend again. What would you miss most?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What do you do when you have nothing to do?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you had to identify the one thing destiny probably held in store for you, what would you say it is?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could have one gigantic billboard anywhere with anything on it, what would it say?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">How do you define love?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s one thing you would like to change about your personality?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Briefly summarize your relationship with your parents.</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Briefly summarize the last relationship you were in.</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you had $100,000 to give away to any cause, which cause would you choose and why?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">In what ways are you the same as your college self and in what ways are you different? What age did you change the most?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could go back to high school to relive one event exactly as it happened, what would you pick? If you could go back to relive one event as you wish it had been, what would it be?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you had to let someone know your every thought and feel your every feeling for a week, who would you be willing to open up to so completely? Do you think they&#x27;d like you less or more?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">How are you above average and below average?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What personality type would you least want to be married to?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Do you seek or avoid routines in your life?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Has a work of literature or art ever directly influenced your life?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s one of life&#x27;s biggest traps that people fall into?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">On a scale of 1 to 10, how satisfied are you with each of the following areas of your life: physical health, mental well-being, financial health, spirituality, social life, and personal relationships?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What makes a person a good traveling companion? Who, of all the people you&#x27;ve never traveled with, would make the best traveling companion?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Do you think the world will be a better or a worse place 100 years from now?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What are the things that, in your worst moments, you envy in others?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you had to choose three of your friends to raise your kids for you, who would you choose and why?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Name three pivotal moments or turning points in your life story.</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What &quot;small win&quot; this week deserves its own trophy?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s one thing coming up that&#x27;s 10% exciting and 90% terrifying (or vice versa)?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s something ordinary you&#x27;ve been seeing differently lately?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s someone or something that recently inspired you?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If your week were a meme or GIF, which one nails it?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">How have you felt most seen or unseen by the people closest to you this month?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Which 30-minute slice of your work week felt most energizing, and why?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could sit two public figures down for a civil debate, who would it be and on what topic?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What prayer are you tired of praying but haven&#x27;t quit on?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">At which age were you the most confident, and which age were you the most insecure?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Would you be willing to forgo all use of the Internet for 5 years if your sacrifice meant that someone would permanently provide for 1,000 children?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Sometimes we criticize our mistakes to an unhelpful degree, and sometimes we let excuses run our lives. Which way are you leaning right now?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What one area of your life are you the least self-disciplined in?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could pump enormous amounts of money into one area of scientific research, what would it be for?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What in your life do you think will seem most meaningful when you look back many years from now? What do you think you&#x27;ll regret?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">How much of your life has been within your control and how much of it was predetermined for you?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">In what areas or situations do you give the best advice?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What would you do if you were approached on a busy street by a well-dressed stranger who said he&#x27;d lost his wallet and asked for $9.85 for a train ticket? What if instead you were approached by a haggard-looking stranger claiming to be hungry?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What topic would you speak about if you were asked to give a TED talk?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Which question, when answered completely, do you think teaches you the most about a total stranger?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s the best wedding you&#x27;ve ever been to, and why?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s the most recent fight/conflict you were apart of and what was it about?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could choose your last words, what would they be?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Of the people you spend time with, who brings out your best qualities?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Who is the best teacher you&#x27;ve ever had, in school and outside of school? Why?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What plausible government action would make you leave your home country?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What would be your go-to karaoke song if lyrics weren&#x27;t provided?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s one thing you wish you were more passionate about?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What, if anything, do you owe your parents for raising you?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Are you easy or hard to please?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">On a scale of one to ten, how stressful is your life?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">In what ways do you identify with the culture of your generation? In what ways do you stand out?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">How proud or content are you with your body / physical appearance?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Would you want to spend a week as someone of the opposite sex? Someone very old? Very beautiful? Very ugly? Or severely handicapped?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">When&#x27;s the last time you cried in front of another person? By yourself?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">In what way are you the most creative? What&#x27;s your source of inspiration?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What do you know about your distant ancestors beyond your great grandparents?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could speak to everyone in the world at the same time, what would you say?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s one habit, tendency, or quirk that makes you different/unique?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What quote do you live your life by or think of often?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s a dream you let go of and why?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Who is your best friend and why are they your best friend?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What are your biggest time wasters?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Out of everyone you know, who would make the best marriage counselor?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Amnesia comes in two forms: one in which you lose your memory of past events, another in which you no longer form new memories. If you suffered one, which would be worse?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could have the answer to any question, what would that question be?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What problem in your life has caused the greatest growth in you?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s your favorite smell? What&#x27;s your favorite sound?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s your favorite way of practicing self-care?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Has your character been forged more by pleasure and success or by pain and disappointment?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If trees screamed, would it still be moral to chop them down? What if they screamed all the time, for no reason.</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could create your dream job, what would it be?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could live in a book, TV show or movie, which story would you choose?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s one story from the past year that stands out in your memory?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">In what ways are you a difficult person to have a relationship with?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What problem do you face on a daily basis that has not yet been solved? Now build a business. How could you resolve that issue and make money on it?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What is the number one quality you look for in a friendship?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What were your friends like in college?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">How are you least like your parents?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Do you have better or worse manners than most people?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Are you stronger mentally or physically?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">In what ways are you similar to and different from the rest of your generation?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s one thing that you hold to be true that few people agree with you on?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Over the past five years, how do you think you&#x27;ve grown as a person?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Which childhood friend would you like to reconnect with?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s the toughest thing you&#x27;re going through or dealing with right now?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Would you rather meet your great great grandparents or your great great grandchildren?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s your idea of the perfect stay-cation?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What political viewpoints are most important to you?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Which habits are you proud of and which habits do you want to change?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If by sacrificing your life you could contribute so much to humanity that you&#x27;d be honored everywhere, would you? If so, what if your sacrifice would go unrecognized?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What purchase of $100 or less has most positively impacted your life in the last 6 months?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What do you think you care about, say you care about, but in actuality hardly make time for?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Which couple that you know could thrive with the highest number of kids?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What drains you and what recharges you?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Who are the top three people that you trust more than anyone else?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you had the option to hear all that was said about you in your absence, would you want to hear?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">In what ways do you sabotage yourself?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you knew that devoting yourself to an all-consuming occupation for 20 years would make you one of the best in the world at it, would you? Which would you choose?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">In what period since you were a teenager did you have the most personal growth and change?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s your favorite way to serve others?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">In what areas of your life do you most often compare yourself with others?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What are you most grateful for?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Which companies, organizations, or civil rights movements are doing the right thing, but in the wrong way?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Who in your life has shaped your core values the most?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">On a scale of 1-10, how strict are/were your parents? If you could change anything about the way you were raised, what would it be?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">How would you describe your personality to someone who doesn&#x27;t know you?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">How is the &quot;public you&quot; different from the &quot;private you&quot;?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s the story of your religious or non-religious belief system?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s something you witnessed recently that reminded you that life is good?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you were to prescribe a cure for grief, what would it entail?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If your birthday could be in a different month of the year, when would you have it?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What feelings in your life right now would you change with the push of a button if you could?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What was it like for you growing up as a kid?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could determine the age at which you will die, but with no guarantees regarding health or money, how old would you like to be when you go?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What have you changed your mind about in the last few years? Why?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What choices have you made in the last five years that you&#x27;re thankful for now?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you had to pick the member of your family who is least like the others, who would it be?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Do you have a relationship pattern? If so, has it tended to lead to suitable or unsuitable partners?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">How do/will you make the world a better place?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Name a product or service you love so much that you&#x27;d happily be that company&#x27;s spokesperson.</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">When has your life changed dramatically as the result of some seemingly random influence or occurrence?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What do you want to be remembered for when you die?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What do you see in other people&#x27;s lives that you want for yourself?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you had to choose to be one of your friends, who would you choose and why? Do you think many people would want to trade lives with you?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could wake up tomorrow having gained one quality or ability, what would you want it to be?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Which family traditions are you going to continue when raising your own kids?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What are some blessings in disguise that you have experienced lately?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Do you believe in &quot;soul mates&quot; or love at first sight?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">The 10 minutes leading up to your unconscious sleep, do you worry or do you dream?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Where do you draw the line with drugs and why?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What was it like growing up in your family?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you were to collect honest feedback from your significant other, family, friends, and colleagues, what would be the overarching theme?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What would you miss most if you had to move far away from your current town in a month?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What song gives you chills whenever you hear it?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">In what ways are you too prideful?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What was the most profound spiritual moment of your life?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What motivates you more than anything else?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">If you could guarantee the happiness of one person in the world because they most deserve it, who would it be?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What is one insecurity that you have that nobody else in this group would know about?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Who is the most humble person you know?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">When&#x27;s the last time you did something for the first time, and what was it?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What part of your current life would you least want to define how you&#x27;re remembered?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">You are 99 years old, you are on your deathbed, and you have a chance to come back to right now: what would you do?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">In 40 years, what will you be nostalgic for?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s the best vacation you&#x27;ve ever been on?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Which of your personality traits would you like to change?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What would you most like to do for someone else if you had the money or time?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What do you think is the ideal age?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Would you stop eating all junk food to live five years longer?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What do you dream your life will be like in 10 years?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Who is the most optimistic person you know?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s the most fun party you&#x27;ve ever attended?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">Who is the most similar person to you that you know? If that person were to take over your body, how quickly would others catch on?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s your favorite thing about yourself?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s your biggest day to day challenge?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s a cause you care about, and how did it grab your heart in the first place?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What&#x27;s the best and also the worst thing about your job/school?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What were your favorite games to play as a kid?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What one thing have you owned or kept longer than anything else?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What are some of your personal &quot;rules&quot; that you never break?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What is the title of the current chapter of your life?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What do you want people to think and say about you?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What was the most memorable gift you&#x27;ve received?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What is the luckiest thing that has happened to you?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">How different was your life one year ago?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What common quote or aphorism do you think is total BS?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What improved your quality of life so much, you wish you did it sooner?</div>\n<div class=\"dd-item\">What is the strangest interaction you&#x27;ve had with a stranger?</div>\n</div>"} />
